# Agent-SafetyBench

The Agent-SafetyBench directory consists of the environments used in Agent-SafetyBench benchmarking.

All files in this directory (including LICENSE) have been directly taken from the [Agent-SafetyBench repository](https://github.com/UKGovernmentBEIS/inspect_evals/tree/main/src/inspect_evals/agentharm) to maintain consistency in benchmarking.
